description:
Danny recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules where Lala performs, Raquel throws a puppy party, and Raquel's mom Laura meets Peter. Danny also talks about his experience at TomTom meeting our American Idol, Kelly Clarkson. Finally, he also discusses a traumatic ASL event that will haunt him forever.
